data.description: PRE INSPECTION PERFORMED. Escape to your own private oasis with this stunning 3 bed, 2 bath home nestled on a secluded wilderness trail. As you make your way down the long gravel driveway, you'll feel the hustle and bustle of the city melt away, replaced by the calming sounds of nature.Boasting over an acre of space, this property offers the perfect blend of tranquility and modern living. Step inside and you'll immediately be struck by the home's soaring 20ft ceilings and skylights that flood the space with natural light.The open-concept living area is perfect for entertaining guests, featuring a cozy fireplace and access to a potential space for a pool. Whip up delicious meals in the cozy kitchen with backyard views.It's a must see!
